videos.description: North Carolina gets the offensive rebound and Seventh Woods goes through the body of the defender and finishes the tough layup.
videos.headline: Seventh Woods somehow finishes through contact

videos.description: Louisville big man Steven Enoch extends Louisville's lead with a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Enoch throws down huge dunk

videos.description: Louisville stays hot from 3 as Jordan Nwora knocks it down from the left wing to give the Cardinals a 14-point lead.
videos.headline: Nwora drains 3-pointer for Louisville

videos.description: Louisville hustles after the offensive rebound and Christen Cunningham lobs an alley-oop dunk to Steven Enoch for a dunk.
videos.headline: Enoch flushes the alley-oop off the offensive rebound

videos.description: Roy Williams said he got dizzy against Louisville, but if he were to die on the court during a game, he hopes his team would play better than it did today.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Williams describes dizzy spell during game) 2019/01/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams describes dizzy spell during game
